title: Shanhai Qi Tan
synopsis: "The Story of the Mountain and the Sea" is a three-dimensional TV cartoon for teenagers between the ages of 12-22 and the theme of fantasy adventure. The story is elaborated with adventure, magic, battle, and humorous plots. It mainly tells the story of the protagonist Peng Lai. The adventure and the monster led by the villain fight wits and bravely, with a wit, brave and optimistic spirit, overcome various difficulties and finally recover the mountain and sea beast. The heroine Peng Lai is a 14-year-old junior high school student. During the summer vacation, Peng Lai traveled alone, and stumbled into a mysterious cave. That cave is actually the ancient remains of the ancient Chinese book "Shan Hai Jing". Peng Lai had long heard that "Shan Hai Jing" was a strange book, so he curiously took down the "Shan Hai Jing" on the altar to read it. Unexpectedly, he unlocked the seal of the book and caused various strange monsters in the Shan Hai Jing. Ran out of the book. The Shanhaijing itself has become a wordless book of heaven. In order to calm the commotion and restore the Shanhaijing, the brave Peng Lai stepped forward and embarked on a journey of recovering the beasts of the mountains and seas and repairing the "Shanhaijing". (translated from tenceng)

title: Yingxiong Fengzicai
synopsis: The film takes the "Chinese Dream" as the theme, with Feng Zicai, a famous anti-familiar general, as the main character. Through the use of high-tech, many tragic scenes from the first and second Opium Wars are presented on the TV screen, and Feng Zicai leads the soldiers to obtain The Zhennanguan Grand Victory "restores the scene" through animation. Feng Zicai was a famous general in the late Qing Dynasty. After the outbreak of the Sino-French War, the 67-year-old veteran Feng Zicai led his army on an expedition. On March 23, 1886, he wiped out the main French army invading the border at Zhennanguan Pass on the Sino-Vietnamese border, and won the famous Zhennanguan victory.  (translated from bilibili)

His father Pi Dawei feels that he doesn’t care enough about his son, so he started a "scientific educational experiment" and used professional parenting books. The way to educate children. title: Shinka no Mi: Shiranai Uchi ni Kachigumi Jinsei
synopsis: "Seiichi Hiiragi is an ugly, revolting, dirty, smelly fatass"—these are the insults hurled at him one after another about his appearance. Such was Seiichi's miserable school life. One day, a voice claiming to be a God announced over the public address system to prepare to be transported to another world. The entire school, including Seiichi, were sent to a fantasy world featuring game-like elements such as levels, stats, and skills. However, the God still had preparations to complete for the transfer, and would send them over as soon as the hero summoning ritual was ready. The classes all formed groups to wait for the transfer, but Seiichi alone was excluded, and as such was summoned to a different area. After being transported, the first thing Seiichi ate was the "Fruit of Evolution," which would come to greatly change his life... This story follows Seiichi from being bullied by his classmates, neglected as a companion, to his hard work, positive attitude, and surviving in this new world. As a result, he becomes one of the champions before he knows it.  (Source: MU, amended)

synopsis: A group of polar bears who lost their homes, according to the legend of their ancestors, found the pure island of the North Pole. The venerable of the Beibei family and the grandfather of Beibei, decided to lead everyone to find the legendary ice diamond. It is said that only the energy of the ice diamond is released , You can save the earth and bring the earth’s climate environment back to the previous normal level. Thus, a journey of finding ice diamonds began. As the inheritor of the polar bear family, Beibei bears the role of pioneer in every exploration. Purity Island is the last land in the Arctic. It is surrounded by icebergs, and there are mysterious plants in the middle. In the process of searching for ice drills, they encountered various animals and had conflicts with them to varying degrees. So much misunderstanding each other. Whether it is an enemy or a friend, everyone gradually understands in the friction... (translated from iqiyi)

Dandanlong, 8 years old, likes to invent and create, and dreams of creating earth-shattering miracles. Xiu Xiulong, 7 years old, is a small partner of Dan Dan Long, often accompanied by Dan Dan Long. Heilong, 8 years old, likes martial arts, always hopes to surpass Dandanlong, but all ended in failure. Ya Yalong, 5 years old, Dan Dan Long’s sister, likes to follow her brother, is Dan Dan Long’s most beloved little sister, clever, naughty, and crying. Little Huo Xian, 6 years old, is a kind of fire fairy with a small body. He likes to imitate others and change some weird things. He is a close-fitting fairy of Dandanlong. Lightspeed dragon, savage, 18 years old, ambitious, and a little clever, always hopes to rule Dragon Turtle Island, but most of the time it is always self-defeating, cleverness is mistaken. Xiao Feilong, Long Feifei, 8 years old, bold, informal, righteous, active, bold, and like to play, is a savage follower, and because he is not rigid, he often does some incredible things that make people laugh. Dragon Turtle Old Man, 1000 (translated from iqiyi)
